      "description": "The Defiance Pure Space Daily 2X Strategy ETF (SPCL) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in stocks based on a particular theme. The fund is actively managed and seeks to  deliver 2x the daily performance of a concentrated portfolio of space-related companies using derivatives. The strategy aims for leveraged exposure to firms involved in satellite systems, launch technologies, and the broader space economy. SPCL was launched on Apr 7, 2026 and is issued by Defiance.",
